title: VA Indie Pop Playlist August 2013 - Get Lucky (Dutch Treat I2 HQ
description:
A quite definite preview of the third Dutch Treat Indie Playlist of August. A difficult month because not much was happening in the Indie world last months.

I must assume that everybody already are enjoying their holidays. Still quite nice though.... Enjoy,
